{"id":232681560,"title":"不專業分享， 西班牙胡米亞DOP哈麥娜Joven紅葡萄酒","content":"最近比較喜歡試沒喝過的酒，所以買了一瓶美聯社DM推的紅酒\n\n葡萄品種是Monstrell加Syrah, Monstrell我從沒喝過，所以第一次喝的感覺蠻特殊的。\n\n酒標上面有寫喝起來有甘油跟葡萄果肉的味道，但甘油的味道我真的不太熟悉，所以在酒開瓶的前一個小時，我真的覺得味道不太順。或許是我比較常喝Cabernet及Merlot吧，對其他品種很陌生，但開瓶後一小時再喝， Syrah的味道就比較明顯，丹寧適中，甜度幾乎沒有，酸度略酸，搭配洋芋片及油膩的鹹酥雞還okay。\n\n價位好像是360吧，如果好奇Monstrell是什麼味道，可以買來一試。\n\n但我個人私心認為400元以下的酒，還是Yellow Tail喝起來比較順。\nhttps://i.imgur.com/HFmX51F.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/LnzofJI.jpg","excerpt":"最近比較喜歡試沒喝過的酒，所以買了一瓶美聯社DM推的紅酒，葡萄品種是Monstrell加Syrah， Monstrell我從沒喝過，所以第一次喝的感覺蠻特殊的。酒標上面有寫喝起來有甘油跟葡萄果肉的味道","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-13T16:12:16.458Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-13T16:12:16.458Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":7,"tags":[],"topics":["品酒板","喝酒","品酒","品酒版","葡萄酒"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"加州大學戴維斯分校","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/HFmX51F.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/LnzofJI.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"bb81eaaa-6311-4a03-94dc-2734575e0c87","url":"https://i.imgur.com/HFmX51Fl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/HFmX51Fl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/HFmX51Fl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2019-12-13T16:12:16.458Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-13T16:12:16.458Z"},{"id":"bb81eaaa-6311-4a03-94dc-2734575e0c87","url":"https://i.imgur.com/HFmX51F.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/HFmX51F","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/HFmX51Fl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":[],"createdAt":"2019-12-13T16:12:16.458Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-13T16:12:16.458Z"},{"id":